entries.title: Tatoo System: Ghost Tide's Black Nemesis
entries.title_d: Kelen Wordkal was right. You've discovered, after a particularly interesting run-in with the Black Nemesis, something more foreboding has been causing the disappearances of the freighters traveling through the Ghost Tide Nebula.
